trans-unit.source: REST API operations for the Batch service return standard HTTP status codes, as defined in the <externalLink><linkText>HTTP/1.1 Status Code Definitions</linkText><linkUri>http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=133333</linkUri></externalLink>.

trans-unit.source: API operations may also return additional error information to provide the developer with more information about the error.
